snippet.title: [GOTY 2013 #9] Best VGM 1502 - Brothers : A Tale of Two Sons - Winged Hope
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC / Xbox 360 / PS3
Brothers : A Tale of Two Son (2013)
Winged Hope
Gustaf Grefberg
